## Plan 2-B: Catalog Selection Interface — Not Started
*Target: Dealers browse and activate manufacturers/products for their site*

### What's Done
- `DealerCatalogSelection` Prisma model exists (`dealerId`, `productId`, `isActive`, `status`)
- `DealerCatalogGroup` and `DealerCatalogGroupProduct` models exist for custom grouping

### Remaining Work
- [ ] Portal — Catalog by Manufacturer (`/portal/catalog`) — browsable manufacturer list with activation toggles
- [ ] Portal — Product Browser (`/portal/catalog/[manufacturerSlug]`) — filterable grid with per-product toggles
- [ ] API routes for catalog selection (bulk activate/deactivate, manufacturer toggle)
- [ ] Auto-log selection changes to `DealerActivityLog`

---

## Plan 2-C: Activity Log & Change Feed — Not Started
*Target: Real-time visibility into every catalog change — our biggest WhyFire differentiator*

### What's Done
- `DealerActivityLog` Prisma model exists with `type`, `title`, `message`, `metadata`, `isRead`
- ScraperEngine writes `AuditLog` entries on product changes (foundation for fan-out)

### Remaining Work
- [ ] Dealer Notification Fan-Out service — after scraper sync, create `DealerActivityLog` entries for affected dealers
- [ ] Portal Activity Feed page (`/portal/activity`) — chronological feed with filters and action buttons
- [ ] API routes for activity feed (list, mark read, take action)
- [ ] Sync Status Widget — per-manufacturer last sync time + status indicator

---

## Plan 2-D: Dashboard, Notifications & Airtable Integration — Partially Started
*Target: Summary dashboard, configurable email alerts, and Airtable client DB sync*

### What's Done
- Dealer settings page at `/dealer/[slug]/settings` — account details, password change
- `src/lib/airtable.ts` — Airtable client utility exists
- `src/lib/crmConnector.ts` — CRM connector stub (HubSpot/Salesforce placeholders)
- `src/lib/emailService.ts` — Email service stub exists

### Remaining Work
- [ ] Portal Dashboard (`/portal/dashboard`) — stats cards, recent activity, sync health panel
- [ ] Notification settings UI — email toggles per event type, frequency preference
- [ ] Notification email system — SendGrid/SES templates for digests and alerts
- [ ] Airtable sync endpoint (`/api/admin/airtable-sync`) — read client records, match/create DealerAccount records
- [ ] Admin "Sync from Airtable" button
